{% doc %}
  @prompt
    
    
    ---
    
    # Customizable Rich Text Section Specification 
    
    ## 1️⃣ Layout Options
    
    **Container Width Settings**
    
    * Option selector:
    
      * Full Width (100%)
      * Boxed (theme default container)
      * Custom Max Width
    * If **Custom Max Width** is selected:
    
      * Enable Max Width input (px)
      * Range: 800px – 1800px
      * Default: 1200px
    * Section must be fully responsive (desktop, tablet, mobile)
    
    ---
    
    ## 2️⃣ Spacing Controls
    
    * Top Padding (separate control)
    * Bottom Padding (separate control)
    * Unit: px (responsive-ready if supported)
    
    ---
    
    ## 3️⃣ Style Controls
    
    * Background Color picker
    * Text Color picker
    * Text Alignment selector:
    
      * Left
      * Center
      * Right
    
    ---
    
    ## 4️⃣ Content Structure
    
    ### 🖼 Image
    
    * Upload image option
    * Image display mode:
    
      * Cover
      * Contain
    * Image size controls:
    
      * Width (px or %)
      * Max-width option
    * Responsive scaling enabled
    
    ### 🏷 Title (Small Label Text)
    
    * Font size control: 10px – 40px
    * Bottom spacing control
    * Styled as paragraph or small heading
    
    ### 📝 Heading
    
    * Selectable tag:
    
      * H2
      * H3
    
    ### 📄 Description
    
    * Short paragraph text
    * Clean readable line-height
    
    ### 🔘 CTA Button (Optional)
    
    * Enable/Disable toggle
    * Button label field
    * Button link field
    * Accessible focus state required
    
    ---
    
    ## 5️⃣ Rich Text Area
    
    * Fully editable WYSIWYG field
    * Custom width control for content area
    * Option to control max-width separately from section width
    
    ---
    
    ## 6️⃣ Layout Behavior
    
    * Desktop:
    
      * Flexible layout (image + text side by side if enabled)
    * Mobile:
    
      * Stacked layout (image above text)
    * Maintain proper spacing between:
    
      * Image
      * Title
      * Heading
      * Paragraph
      * Button
    
    ---
    
    ## 7️⃣ Design Requirements
    
    * Clean vertical rhythm
    * Consistent spacing system
    * Mobile-first responsive structure
    * Accessibility best practices:
    
      * Proper heading hierarchy
      * Alt text required for image
      * Button accessible via keyboard
      * Sufficient color contrast
    
    
    
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-rich-text-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding-top: {{ block.settings.padding_top }}px;
    padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.padding_bottom }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-rich-text-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    {% if block.settings.container_width == 'full' %}
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 100%;
      padding-left: 20px;
      padding-right: 20px;
    {% elsif block.settings.container_width == 'boxed' %}
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      padding-left: 20px;
      padding-right: 20px;
    {% else %}
      width: 100%;
      max-width: {{ block.settings.custom_max_width }}px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      padding-left: 20px;
      padding-right: 20px;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-rich-text-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: {{ block.settings.text_alignment }};
  }

  .ai-rich-text-layout-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .ai-rich-text-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .ai-rich-text-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.image_width }}%;
    max-width: {{ block.settings.image_max_width }}px;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    {% if block.settings.text_alignment == 'center' %}
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    {% elsif block.settings.text_alignment == 'right' %}
      margin-left: auto;
    {% endif %}
    object-fit: {{ block.settings.image_display_mode }};
  }

  .ai-rich-text-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.image_width }}%;
    max-width: {{ block.settings.image_max_width }}px;
    {% if block.settings.text_alignment == 'center' %}
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    {% elsif block.settings.text_alignment == 'right' %}
      margin-left: auto;
    {% endif %}
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .ai-rich-text-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-rich-text-text-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .ai-rich-text-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_font_size }}px;
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.title_spacing }}px 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .ai-rich-text-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-rich-text-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .ai-rich-text-richtext-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.richtext_max_width }}px;
    {% if block.settings.text_alignment == 'center' %}
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    {% elsif block.settings.text_alignment == 'right' %}
      margin-left: auto;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-rich-text-richtext-{{ ai_gen_id }} p {
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .ai-rich-text-richtext-{{ ai_gen_id }} p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .ai-rich-text-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 12px 32px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_background_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 14px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .ai-rich-text-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_text_color }};
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-rich-text-layout-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      {% if block.settings.desktop_layout == 'side-by-side' %}
        flex-direction: row;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 48px;
      {% endif %}
    }

    .ai-rich-text-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      {% if block.settings.desktop_layout == 'side-by-side' %}
        flex: 0 0 40%;
      {% endif %}
    }

    .ai-rich-text-text-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      {% if block.settings.desktop_layout == 'side-by-side' %}
        flex: 1;
      {% endif %}
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<ai-rich-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-rich-text-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-rich-text-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-rich-text-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-rich-text-layout-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.show_image %}
          <div class="ai-rich-text-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% if block.settings.image %}
              <img
                src="{{ block.settings.image | image_url: width: 2000 }}"
                alt="{{ block.settings.image.alt | escape }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="{{ block.settings.image.width }}"
                height="{{ block.settings.image.height }}"
                class="ai-rich-text-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              >
            {% else %}
              <div class="ai-rich-text-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ai-rich-text-text-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.title != blank %}
            <p class="ai-rich-text-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.title }}</p>
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
            {% if block.settings.heading_tag == 'h2' %}
              <h2 class="ai-rich-text-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
            {% else %}
              <h3 class="ai-rich-text-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h3>
            {% endif %}
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings.description != blank %}
            <p class="ai-rich-text-description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.description }}</p>
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings.richtext != blank %}
            <div class="ai-rich-text-richtext-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.richtext }}
            </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings.show_button and block.settings.button_label != blank %}
            <a
              href="{{ block.settings.button_link }}"
              class="ai-rich-text-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
              {{ block.settings.button_label }}
            </a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</ai-rich-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class AiRichText{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
      }

      connectedCallback() {
      }
    }

    customElements.define('ai-rich-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}', AiRichText{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Rich text",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Layout"
    },
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "container_width",
      "label": "Container width",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "full",
          "label": "Full width"
        },
        {
          "value": "boxed",
          "label": "Boxed"
        },
        {
          "value": "custom",
          "label": "Custom max width"
        }
      ],
      "default": "boxed"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "custom_max_width",
      "label": "Custom max width",
      "min": 800,
      "max": 1800,
      "step": 50,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 1200
    },
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "desktop_layout",
      "label": "Desktop layout",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "stacked",
          "label": "Stacked"
        },
        {
          "value": "side-by-side",
          "label": "Side by side"
        }
      ],
      "default": "stacked"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "desktop_width_percent",
      "label": "Desktop width",
      "min": 50,
      "max": 100,
      "step": 5,
      "unit": "%",
      "default": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Spacing"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "padding_top",
      "label": "Top padding",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 100,
      "step": 4,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 40
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "padding_bottom",
      "label": "Bottom padding",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 100,
      "step": 4,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 40
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Style"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "background_color",
      "label": "Background",
      "default": "#ffffff"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "text_color",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "#000000"
    },
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "text_alignment",
      "label": "Text alignment",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "left",
          "label": "Left"
        },
        {
          "value": "center",
          "label": "Center"
        },
        {
          "value": "right",
          "label": "Right"
        }
      ],
      "default": "left"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Image"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_image",
      "label": "Show image",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "image",
      "label": "Image"
    },
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "image_display_mode",
      "label": "Display mode",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "cover",
          "label": "Cover"
        },
        {
          "value": "contain",
          "label": "Contain"
        }
      ],
      "default": "cover"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "image_width",
      "label": "Width",
      "min": 20,
      "max": 100,
      "step": 5,
      "unit": "%",
      "default": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "image_max_width",
      "label": "Max width",
      "min": 200,
      "max": 1000,
      "step": 50,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 600
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Title"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title",
      "label": "Title"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "title_font_size",
      "label": "Font size",
      "min": 10,
      "max": 40,
      "step": 2,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 14
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "title_spacing",
      "label": "Bottom spacing",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 40,
      "step": 4,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 8
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Heading"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "Rich text"
    },
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "heading_tag",
      "label": "Heading tag",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "h2",
          "label": "H2"
        },
        {
          "value": "h3",
          "label": "H3"
        }
      ],
      "default": "h2"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Description"
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "description",
      "label": "Description",
      "default": "Share information about your brand with your customers."
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Rich text content"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "richtext",
      "label": "Rich text",
      "default": "<p>Use this text to share information about your brand with your customers. Describe a product, share announcements, or welcome customers to your store.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "richtext_max_width",
      "label": "Content max width",
      "min": 400,
      "max": 1200,
      "step": 50,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 800
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Button"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_button",
      "label": "Show button",
      "default": false
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "button_label",
      "label": "Button label",
      "default": "Learn more"
    },
    {
      "type": "url",
      "id": "button_link",
      "label": "Button link"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "button_background_color",
      "label": "Button background",
      "default": "#000000"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "button_text_color",
      "label": "Button text",
      "default": "#ffffff"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "button_hover_color",
      "label": "Button hover background",
      "default": "#333333"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "button_hover_text_color",
      "label": "Button hover text",
      "default": "#ffffff"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Rich text"
    }
  ],
  "tag": null
}
{% endschema %}